(36689, 11164, 3518, 1, '自由沉默', '(Inspired by Patti LaBelle''s "Love, Need and Want You," 台灣電視新聞 & "濕地．石化．島嶼想像")\r\n\r\nLyrics: Brien John\r\nMusic: Brien John & CJ\r\nProduced by Trying Times\r\nArranged by Trying Times\r\nKeyboards: CJ\r\nGuitars: 安通尼\r\nBass: Dawson\r\nDrums: Saul\r\nHorn Arrangement: CJ\r\nLead Vocals: B-jam, 大樹 & Sebastian\r\nBackground Vocals: B-jam, 大樹, Sebastian Wang & Frank\r\nBackground Vocal Arrangements: B-jam\r\n\r\nⒸ2011 TriTones Productions', '2011-06-30 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 2, '開心　是你追尋的態度\r\n你說生活不該太嚴肅\r\n前進　用差不多的速度\r\n不要停在無謂的關注\r\n世界有太多問題\r\n你也知道反正總會有人擔心\r\n最好保持適當的距離\r\n如果末日真的降臨\r\n就當作旅行\r\n\r\n(Gotta go, we''re wasting time)\r\n(For I know) 沉默就是按下按鈕\r\n(Don''t say no, unless we try)\r\n(In our lives)\r\n\r\n終有一種遺憾　來得太晚\r\n終有一片草原　失去空間\r\n那時候的明白轉圜\r\nBut we can''t come back\r\n\r\n相信　決定了你的眼睛\r\n或是誰該負責最近的壞天氣\r\n消息　標題　只是綜藝\r\n但是我們都有插手的權利', '', 286, '', 'Brien John & CJ', 'Brien John', 'Trying Times', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-06-30 20:25:41', '2015-03-12 13:47:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
