(36697, 11164, 0, 3, 'Alright', '(Inspired by Joshua Redman Elastic Band''s "Can a Good Thing Last Forever," Ledisi''s "Goin'' Through Changes" & 詹宏志''s "城市人")\r\n\r\nLyrics: Brien John\r\nMusic: Trying Times\r\nProduced by Trying Times\r\nArranged by Trying Times\r\nKeyboards: CJ\r\nGuitars: 安通尼\r\nBass: Dawson\r\nDrums: Saul\r\nLead Vocals: B-jam & Frank\r\nBackground Vocals: B-jam, 大樹, Sebastian Wang & Frank\r\nBackground Vocal Arrangements: B-jam\r\n\r\nⒸ2011 TriTones Productions', '2011-06-30 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 2, '一而再地想離開\r\n又不自禁留下來\r\n這樣反覆　妳說alright\r\n沒能夠逃避　妳的愛　我的難堪\r\n在迂迴　進退　之間\r\n還是相信妳的美\r\n妳有太多脾氣　難題\r\n也總想回到過去\r\n世界卻不放棄讓妳前進\r\n而我只能把妳抱緊\r\n堅定說　妳就是我　完整的原因\r\n\r\nYour body''s got me feeling alright\r\n\r\n遠來的人說　妳冷漠　妳厭舊　（不回頭）\r\n不懂生活　以為匆忙是精采\r\n散步逛街當作競賽\r\n別在意　因為我知道妳有妳的美麗\r\n讓我脫下妳的外衣\r\n\r\nYour body''s got me feeling alright\r\n\r\n當妳哭泣　我傷心\r\n因為這不是單純選擇的遊戲\r\n其實除了妳我也無處可去\r\n用註定的姿勢愛著妳\r\n\r\n我只想留在這裡\r\n\r\nYour body''s got me feeling alright', '', 388, '', 'Brien John & Trying Times', 'Brien John', 'Trying Times', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2011-06-30 23:49:51', '2013-10-07 17:18:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
